在最初，製作群方面宣佈的[[配音|配音者]]是百老匯演員[[克莉絲汀·肯諾維斯|克莉絲汀·肯諾維斯]]<ref name="chenowethkillermovies">{{cite web|title=Kristin Chenoweth Talks On 'Rapunzel Unbraided'|url=http://www.killermovies.com/r/rapunzelunbraided/articles/4765.html|work=Killermovies.com|publisher=KillerMovies.com|accessdate=2013-05-12|date=2004-12-28|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114014048/http://www.killermovies.com/r/rapunzelunbraided/articles/4765.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rapunzelplaybill">{{cite web|last=Peter|first=Thomas|title=Disney's "Rapunzel" Title Turns Up "Tangled"|url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/136947-Disneys-Rapunzel-Title-Turns-Up-Tangled|work=Playbill.com|publisher=Playbill, Inc|accessdate=2013-05-11|date=2010-02-16|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029195321/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/136947-Disneys-Rapunzel-Title-Turns-Up-Tangled|archivedate=2013-10-29}}</ref><ref name="metromixtangled">{{cite web|last=Berkshire|first=Geoff|title='Tangled' review|url=http://newyork.metromix.com/movies/movie_review/tangled-review/2322271/content|work=Metromix|publisher=Metromix.com|accessdate=2013-05-11|date=2010-11-22|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110803051346/http://newyork.metromix.com/movies/movie_review/tangled-review/2322271/content|archivedate=2011-08-03}}</ref>，之後他們更有一短暫時期相中女演員[[瑞絲·薇斯朋|瑞絲·薇斯朋]]來擔當此角<ref name="witherspoontangledmovieweb">{{cite web|last=Jacobs|first=Evan|title=First Look at Disney's Tangled Trailer|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/first-look-at-disneys-tangled-trailer|work=Movieweb.com|publisher=MovieWeb™, Inc|accessdate=2013-06-22|date=2010-03-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014031239/http://www.movieweb.com/news/first-look-at-disneys-tangled-trailer|archivedate=2013-10-14}}</ref>，但最終她仍未出任配音工作<ref name="witherspoonmoviefone">{{cite web|last=Fischer|first=Martha|title=More problems for Disney - is Rapunzel Unbraided already in trouble?|url=http://news.moviefone.com/2005/11/04/more-problems-for-disney-is-rapunzel-unbraided-already-in-trou/|work=Moviefone.com|publisher=Aol Inc|accessdate=2013-06-24|author=|date=2005-11-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002113838/http://news.moviefone.com/2005/11/04/more-problems-for-disney-is-rapunzel-unbraided-already-in-trou/|archivedate=2013-10-02}}</ref>。在物色過數百名人選之後<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.geeksofdoom.com/2011/03/27/interview-tangled-directors-talk-about-creating-disneys-50th-animated-feature|title = Interview: ‘Tangled’ Directors Talk About Creating Disney’s 50th Animated Feature|accessdate = 2013-08-01|date = 2011-03-27|website = Geeks of Doom|publisher = Geeks of Doom}}</ref>，最終選中了錄音藝人、創作歌手兼女演員[[曼蒂·摩爾|曼蒂·摩爾]]。根據副導霍華德所說，因為她「嗓音中帶有如此絕妙的靈魂」，及「純樸、[[鄰家女孩_(人物)|鄰家女孩]]般的特質，使她具備了迪士尼片中女主角所需的任何條件」<ref name="behindtangledabout">{{cite web|last=Nusair|first=David|title=Behind the Scenes of 'Tangled'|url=http://movies.about.com/od/rapunzel/a/making-of-tangled.htm|work=About.com|publisher=About.com|accessdate=2013-05-11|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029190548/http://movies.about.com/od/rapunzel/a/making-of-tangled.htm|archivedate=2013-10-29}}</ref>。

從小便熱愛迪士尼動畫片的曼蒂·摩爾，將這次得到配音工作的參與機會形容為「無上的夢幻」<ref name=mooremovieweb/>。她在初期因為聽說樂佩一角的配音甄試相當競爭激烈，而幾無意願加入，害怕落選之後只會純粹帶來失望<ref name="moorehuffpost">{{cite web|title=Mandy Moore On Tangled: 'I Screamed As Soon As I Found Out' (INTERVIEW)|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2011/10/19/mandy-moore-on-tangled_n_1019215.html|work=The Huffington Post|publisher=TheHuffingtonPost.com, Inc|accessdate=2013-05-11|date=2011-10-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213012035/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2011/10/19/mandy-moore-on-tangled_n_1019215.html|archivedate=2013-12-13}}</ref><ref name="mooremoviesonline">{{cite web|title=Mandy Moore Interview, TANGLED|url=http://www.moviesonline.ca/2010/11/mandy-moore-interview-tangled/|work=Movies Online|publisher=MoviesOnline|accessdate=2013-03-17|date=2013-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218090604/http://www.moviesonline.ca/2010/11/mandy-moore-interview-tangled/|archivedate=2013-12-18}}</ref>。在下定決心參加後，據說摩爾以近乎「窮追」的方式來爭取這個機會，參加了兩次試音甄試。由於《魔髮奇緣》一片被設定為[[歌舞片|歌舞片]]，因此參選者都必須進行說、唱兩方面的試驗。甄試時，在評審要求以[[唱作人|創作歌手風]]試唱的情形下<ref name="mooree!">{{cite web|last=Malkin|first=Marc|title=Mandy Moore & Hubby: "We Work Well Together"|url=http://ca.eonline.com/news/212920/mandy-moore-hubby-we-work-well-together|work=E!|publisher=E! Entertainment Television, LLC|accessdate=2013-05-11|date=2010-11-26}}</ref>，摩爾表演了自己在2003年專輯《{{lang|en|Coverage}}》中的《{{lang|en|Help Me}}》，其翻唱自[[瓊尼·米歇爾|瓊尼·米歇爾]]的同名經典歌曲<ref name="digitalspymandy">{{cite web|last=Reynolds|first=Simon|title=Mandy Moore ('Tangled')|url=http://www.digitalspy.ca/movies/interviews/a299784/mandy-moore-tangled.html|work=Digital Spy|publisher=Hearst Magazines UK|accessdate=2012-12-29|date=2011-01-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141103223807/http://www.digitalspy.ca/movies/interviews/a299784/mandy-moore-tangled.html|archivedate=2014-11-03}}</ref><ref name="coverageallmusic">{{cite web|title=Coverage|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/coverage-mw0000693728|work=Allmusic|publisher=Rovi Corp|accessdate=2013-03-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130126074010/http://www.allmusic.com/album/coverage-mw0000693728|archivedate=2013-01-26}}</ref><ref name="moorecoveragebillboard">{{cite web|title=Mandy Moore Goes Under 'Covers'|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/70024/mandy-moore-goes-under-covers|work=Billboard|publisher=Billboard|accessdate=2013-06-26|year=2003|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614193642/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/70024/mandy-moore-goes-under-covers|archivedate=2014-06-14}}</ref>。

當加入《魔髮奇緣》的配音陣容後，摩爾還不知道自己參與的將是迪士尼動畫工作室的第50部經典動畫長片。此後她很感激自己對此一無所知，解釋道：「我覺得很幸運，因為若是在開始配音工作前就知道這件事的話，就將受到更大的壓力。」<ref name="mooremoviesonline" />。之後，她也因為發現自己大部份的配音都不會與另兩名主要配音員——[[柴克·萊威|柴克·萊威]]（飾費林·雷德）和[[唐娜·墨菲|唐娜·墨菲]]（飾葛索媽媽）一起在場進行錄製，而感到驚訝。據說配音過程期間，摩爾僅有在錄製片中的男女對唱曲《{{lang|en|[[I_See_the_Light|I See the Light]]}}》時才與萊威碰到面<ref name="mooremovieweb">{{cite web|last=Philbrick|first=Jami|title=EXCLUSIVE: Mandy Moore Talks Tangled|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/exclusive-mandy-moore-talks-tangled|work=MovieWeb|publisher=MovieWeb, Inc|accessdate=2013-05-11|date=2010-11-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054426/http://www.movieweb.com/news/exclusive-mandy-moore-talks-tangled|archivedate=2013-09-21}}</ref>，而摩爾之後上「[[艾倫·狄珍妮秀|艾倫·狄珍妮秀]]」時，也表示自己與墨菲更是到影片上映前一個月的某次記者會才相見<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GBX4wMEnZHk Mandy Moore on Ellen - YouTube] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921061517/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GBX4wMEnZHk |date=2013-09-21 }}</ref>。摩爾亦形容配音錄製的過程具有相當的挑戰性，因為配音時幾乎無法看到劇中的動畫畫面。她之後接受[[英國|英國]]{{Link-en|NOW雜誌|NOW (UK magazine)}}訪問時提到：「可供我揣摩的就只有幾張草圖而已，但配音過程也因此變得很有趣，因為這樣讓我可以進入更深的想像空間中」。而在被問及如何創造出樂佩的嗓音時，摩爾說自己純粹就「豁出去」<ref name="mandymoorenow">{{cite web|title=Tangled star Mandy Moore: I'd like to think I look like Rapunzel|url=http://www.nowmagazine.co.uk/celebrity-news/531660/tangled-star-mandy-moore-i-d-like-to-think-i-look-like-rapunzel|work=Now|publisher=IPC Media Fashion & Beauty Network|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2011-10-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054308/http://www.nowmagazine.co.uk/celebrity-news/531660/tangled-star-mandy-moore-i-d-like-to-think-i-look-like-rapunzel|archivedate=2013-09-21}}</ref>。她經常被要求將同一段台詞重配至最多四遍，直到導演滿意為止。摩爾表示當她首次看到自己配音的成品搭配動畫播映時，心裡想的是「天啊，我的聲音真的很尖」<ref name="mooreleviabout">{{cite web|last=Murray|first=Rebecca|title=Exclusive Interview with Mandy Moore and Zachary Levi from 'Tangled'|url=http://movies.about.com/od/rapunzel/a/Mandy-Moore-Zachary-Levi-Tangled-Interview.htm|work=About.com|publisher=About.com|accessdate=2013-03-30|year=2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130424104056/http://movies.about.com/od/rapunzel/a/Mandy-Moore-Zachary-Levi-Tangled-Interview.htm|archivedate=2013-04-24}}</ref>。

