葛連·基恩在擔任擔任樂佩的角色動畫總監時，曾在{{Link-en|迪士尼九元老|Disney's Nine Old Men}}之一的資深動畫師——{{Link-en|奧立·強司頓|Ollie Johnston}}指導下進行角色設計<ref name="johnstonlatimes">{{cite web|last=Solomon|first=Charles|title=Last of Disney's 'Nine Old Men' dies|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/apr/16/local/me-johnston16|work=Los Angeles Times|publisher=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2013-05-12|date=2008-04-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724100937/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/apr/16/local/me-johnston16|archivedate=2013-07-24}}</ref><ref name="birdjohnstoncartoonbrew">{{cite web|title=Brad Bird on Ollie Johnston|url=http://www.cartoonbrew.com/disney/brad-bird-on-ollie-johnston-5482.html|work=Cartoon Brew|publisher=Cartoon Brew, LLC|accessdate=2013-05-12|date=2008-04-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607054332/http://www.cartoonbrew.com/disney/brad-bird-on-ollie-johnston-5482.html|archivedate=2013-06-07}}</ref>。在看過基恩對樂佩的鉛筆稿測試（{{lang|en|pencil test}}）後，強司頓建議基恩，在捕捉她的動作時不是僅有呈現她在做的事情，還要融入她內心的想法。強司頓說道：「我感好奇的是，她''在想些什麼''？」<ref name="keanedenofgeek">{{cite web|last=Brew|first=Simon|title=Disney legend Glen Keane interview: Tangled, computer animation, his heart attack, and Ollie Johnston|url=http://www.denofgeek.com/movies/16686/disney-legend-glen-keane-interview-tangled-computer-animation-his-heart-attack-and-ollie-johnston|work=Den of Geek|publisher=Dennis Publishing Limited|accessdate=2013-05-11|date=2010-11-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605195703/http://www.denofgeek.com/movies/16686/disney-legend-glen-keane-interview-tangled-computer-animation-his-heart-attack-and-ollie-johnston|archivedate=2013-06-05}}</ref>。基恩後來把強司頓的建議比喻作「讓我無法忘懷的一記當頭棒喝，因此之後當我在繪製人類主題的作品時，總試著進入該角色的中心想法」<ref name="awnkeane">{{cite web|last=Desowitz|first=Bill|title=Glen Keane Talks Tangled|url=http://www.awn.com/articles/article/glen-keane-talks-tangled/page/2%2C1|work=Animation World Network|publisher=AWN, Inc|accessdate=2013-05-11|date=2010-10-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029193355/http://www.awn.com/articles/article/glen-keane-talks-tangled/page/2%2C1|archivedate=2013-10-29}}</ref>。

至於副導拜倫·霍華德個人則是被1989年迪士尼動畫[[小美人魚|小美人魚]]中的女主角，即同樣由基恩創造出來的愛麗兒所激發。根據霍華德的闡述，「愛麗兒是第一個讓我覺得在眼神裡流露著靈魂的角色...我們也希望讓樂佩的眼裡能找到吸引人的靈魂和深情」。另一方面，希望能「將手繪帶入電腦」<ref name="tangledhollywoodnews">{{cite web|last=McCabe|first=Katie|title=THN talks TANGLED with star Mandy Moore and Disney’s directorial golden boys|url=http://www.thehollywoodnews.com/2011/01/30/thn-talks-tangled-star-mandy-moore-disneys-directorial-golden-boys/|work=The Hollywood News|publisher=The Hollywood News 2013|accessdate=2013-06-22|date=2011-01-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302085718/http://www.thehollywoodnews.com/2011/01/30/thn-talks-tangled-star-mandy-moore-disneys-directorial-golden-boys/|archivedate=2014-03-02}}</ref>的基恩，也提到了小美人魚愛麗兒和長髮公主樂佩的相似性，說這兩位女主角同樣「被藩籬隔閡而無法享受夢想，且都懷有不容被壓抑的精神」<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.dvdizzy.com/tangled-glenkeane-interview.html|title = Interview: Tangled Executive Producer and Animation Supervisor Glen Keane|accessdate = 2013-08-01|date = 2011-04-05|website = DVDizzy|publisher = DVDizzy.com|last = Bonanno|first = Luke|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130508013212/http://www.dvdizzy.com/tangled-glenkeane-interview.html|archivedate = 2013-05-08}}</ref>。當設計角色時，基恩受一本介紹「女性美」（{{lang|en|feminine beauty}}）的書影響。在將書中「美的關鍵在於女性面龐上的奇特性」這個概念納入考量後，基恩使樂佩的外貌帶有些微的[[不對稱|不對稱]]，在面容上也有數處程度微小的缺陷，例如刻意被設計到略為突出的門牙、鼻子週邊分布的[[雀斑|雀斑]]等<ref name="tangledtoonbarn">{{cite web|title=Discuss Disney’s Tangled with Byron Howard and Nathan Greno|url=http://www.toonbarn.com/naruto/discuss-disneys-tangled-byron-howard-nathan-greno/|work=ToonBarn|publisher=ToonBarn|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2011-07-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141103223054/http://www.toonbarn.com/naruto/discuss-disneys-tangled-byron-howard-nathan-greno/|archivedate=2014-11-03}}</ref>。基恩也將樂佩的雙眼畫大，以讓她增添些許「不受拘束」的氣質。動畫師們總共創造出了9個版本的樂佩，才決定出最受滿意的設計<ref name=tangleddailymail/>。

