《魔髮奇緣》執行製作人[[約翰·拉薩特|約翰·拉薩特]]有次向[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]解釋道：「挑戰在於，你想讓樂佩這個18年來足不出戶的女孩子，能令人覺得像是個聰明伶俐、有教養、健康而又有趣的人類」<ref name=tanglednytimes/>。為了避免創造出來的是個「過度公主氣又孤僻」的女主角，製作人員在設定樂佩的角色性格時，略為參考了一些女性名人，如作為創意靈感的女演員瑞絲·薇斯朋、[[娜塔莉·波曼|娜塔莉·波曼]]，及「[[週六夜現場|週六夜現場]]」演員班底中的[[艾米·波勒|艾米·波勒]]。結果使樂佩融入了些許「難以捉摸和古靈精怪」的氣質，以「重塑人們以往對公主的印象」<ref name="tangleddailymail">{{cite web|last=Das|first=Lina|title=After a decade of bad hair days, Disney has finally made Tangled, a film about Rapunzel!|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/reviews/article-1351268/Disney-finally-Tangled-film-Rapunzel-decade-bad-hair-days.html|work=Daily Mail|publisher=Associated Newspapers Ltd|accessdate=2013-06-22|date=2011-01-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140119034829/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/reviews/article-1351268/Disney-finally-Tangled-film-Rapunzel-decade-bad-hair-days.html|archivedate=2014-01-19}}</ref>。紐約時報亦提到樂佩這樣的性格是一次顯著的變更，與先前迪士尼動畫的諸位女主角區別開來了。紐約時報評論家巴恩斯（{{lang|en|Brooks Barnes}}）指出樂佩「相當剛強；她在費林爬到她的塔內時，用[[平底鍋|平底鍋]]把他敲到眼花，而且用起頭髮來像是甩長鞭一樣」<ref name="tanglednytimes">{{cite news|last=Barnes|first=Brooks|title=Disney Ties Lots of Hopes to Lots of Hair|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/21/movies/21tangled.html?pagewanted=all|work=The New York Times|publisher=The New York Times Company|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2010-11-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120809081514/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/11/21/movies/21tangled.html?pagewanted=all|archivedate=2012-08-09}}</ref>。而根據曼蒂·摩爾的說法，樂佩「並不是...典型的迪士尼公主...她很獨立自主，可以照顧好自己」<ref name="mtvmandy">{{cite web|last=Warner|first=Kara|title=Mandy Moore's 'Tangled' Heroine Not 'Typical Disney Princess'|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1646720/mandy-moores-tangled-heroine-not-typical-disney-princess.jhtml|work=MTV|publisher=Viacom International Inc|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2010-08-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105163642/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1646720/mandy-moores-tangled-heroine-not-typical-disney-princess.jhtml|archivedate=2013-11-05}}</ref>。

實際上，角色動畫總監葛連·基恩，本身就因為曾將自己的數位家人作為基礎來創造角色而聞名，如小美人魚愛麗兒的外型便是參考他的妻子<ref name="glenkeaneabc">{{cite web|last=Wagons|first=Henry|title=Henry's Disney dreams come true|url=http://www.abc.net.au/arts/stories/s3133247.htm|work=ABC|publisher=ABC|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2011-02-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141202195552/http://www.abc.net.au/arts/stories/s3133247.htm|archivedate=2014-12-02}}</ref>。而本片中，樂佩對於藝術和創作的熱情則是參考自他的女兒克萊兒·基恩（{{lang|en|Claire Keane}}）<ref name="keanemovieweb">{{cite web|last=Gallagher|first=Brian|title=Glen Keane Talks Tangled|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/glen-keane-talks-tangled|work=MovieWeb|publisher=MovieWeb, Inc|accessdate=2013-05-12|date=2011-03-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140806053134/http://www.movieweb.com/news/glen-keane-talks-tangled|archivedate=2014-08-06}}</ref>，樂佩在高塔家中的壁畫和天花板上所塗的圖案，也都是克萊兒的作品<ref name="clairekeanedisney">{{cite web|title=About the Film - Fun Facts|url=http://www.disney.co.uk/tangled/about.jsp|work=Disney.com|publisher=Disney|accessdate=2013-06-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120913073354/http://www.disney.co.uk/tangled/about.jsp|archivedate=2012-09-13}}</ref>。而基恩忙於《魔髮奇緣》製作期間，克萊兒替他生下的孫女瑪諦斯（{{lang|en|Matisse}}）則被當成靈感來創造嬰孩時期的樂佩<ref name="toonzonekeane">{{cite web|last=Liu|first=Ed|title=A Virtual Roundtable with "Tangled" Animation Supervisor Glen Keane|url=http://www.toonzone.net/2011/04/a-virtual-roundtable-with-tangled-animation-supervisor-glen-keane/#.UY7rbkquqPw|work=Toon Zone News|publisher=Genesis Framework|accessdate=2013-05-12|date=2011-04-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210200035/http://www.toonzone.net/2011/04/a-virtual-roundtable-with-tangled-animation-supervisor-glen-keane/#.UY7rbkquqPw|archivedate=2013-12-10}}</ref><ref name="keanejimhill">{{cite web|last=Hill|first=Jim|title=Three Keanes help make Disney's "Tangled" a pretty keen animated comedy|url=http://jimhillmedia.com/editor_in_chief1/b/jim_hill/archive/2010/11/30/-disney-s-tangled--_7C00_-three-keanes-help-make-a-pretty-keen-animated-comedy.aspx#.UcULRdjNkuU|work=Jim Hill Media|publisher=Jim Hill Media|accessdate=2013-06-22|date=2010-11-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120721061745/http://jimhillmedia.com/editor_in_chief1/b/jim_hill/archive/2010/11/30/-disney-s-tangled--_7C00_-three-keanes-help-make-a-pretty-keen-animated-comedy.aspx#.UcULRdjNkuU|archivedate=2012-07-21}}</ref>。
