|}

樂佩是繼1959年[[睡美人_(電影)|睡美人]]女主角奧蘿拉（{{lang|en|Aurora}}）後，多年來迪士尼的第一位[[金髮|金髮]]女主角<ref name="firstblonde">{{cite web|last=Robertson|first=Lindsay|title=First Photos From Disney's Rapunzel: Finally, A Blonde Disney Heroine!|url=http://jezebel.com/5327151/first-photos-from-disneys-rapunzel-finally-a-blonde-disney-heroine/|work=Jezebel|publisher=Gawker Media|accessdate=2013-06-27|date=2009-07-31|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130917012506/http://jezebel.com/5327151/first-photos-from-disneys-rapunzel-finally-a-blonde-disney-heroine/|archivedate=2013-09-17}}</ref>。利用[[電腦生成圖像|電腦生成圖像]]（{{lang|en|CGI}}）技術繪出她的長髮，在《魔髮奇緣》一片的製作中已被普遍認為是最具挑戰性的環節<ref name="criticizethiskeane">{{cite web|last=McKechnie|first=Brian|title=Interview: Animator Glen Keane talks ‘Tangled’|url=http://www.criticizethis.ca/2011/04/interview-animator-glen-keane-talks-%E2%80%98tangled%E2%80%99.html/all/1|work=Criticize This|publisher=Criticize This!|accessdate=2013-05-11|date=2011-04-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927145612/http://www.criticizethis.ca/2011/04/interview-animator-glen-keane-talks-%E2%80%98tangled%E2%80%99.html/all/1/|archivedate=2013-09-27}}</ref>。據《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》報導，首席動畫師葛連·基恩已經因為製作過迪士尼系列電影中數個「最偉大的毛髮作品」而揚名，當中包括了小美人魚愛麗兒、《[[美女與野獸_(1991年電影)|美女與野獸]]》中的野獸、《[[风中奇缘_(电影)|風中奇緣]]》中的[[寶嘉康蒂|寶嘉康蒂]]<ref name="rapunzelhairlatimes">{{cite web|last=Keegan|first=Rebecca|title=The hairy task of creating Rapunzel in 'Tangled'|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2010/11/tangled-hair.html|work=Los Angeles Times|publisher=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2013-06-22|date=2010-11-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131001220033/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2010/11/tangled-hair.html|archivedate=2013-10-01}}</ref>。對於樂佩的長髮，基恩形容它「提醒人們樂佩是被天生賦予魔力的」<ref name="keanecollider">{{cite web|last=Graham|first=Bill|title=Animation Director Glen Keane Exclusive Interview TANGLED|url=http://collider.com/glen-keane-interview-tangled/|work=Collider|publisher=Collider.com|accessdate=2013-06-21|year=2008|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523004216/http://collider.com/glen-keane-interview-tangled|archivedate=2013-05-23}}</ref>，霍華德則打趣地戲稱這長髮本身就可以成為一獨立的角色<ref name=tangleddailymail/>。霍華德與格萊諾規定麾下的動畫師以實物當參考，以構思如何呈現樂佩的長髮及它運動的形態，例如將串好的長繩綁在[[棒球帽|棒球帽]]後、戴著它到處走動，甚至招募多年沒剪髮的女性進入團隊，充當真人模特兒<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Exclusive-Interview-Tangled-Directors-Nathan-Greno-And-Byron-Howard-21861.html|title = Exclusive Interview: Tangled Directors Nathan Greno And Byron Howard|date = 2010-11-23|accessdate = 2013-08-01|website = Cinema Blend|publisher = Cinema Blend LLC|last = Eisenberg|first = Eric|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130923080450/http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Exclusive-Interview-Tangled-Directors-Nathan-Greno-And-Byron-Howard-21861.html|archivedate = 2013-09-23}}</ref>。

[[北卡羅萊納大學|北卡羅萊納大學]]畢業的資深[[軟體工程師|軟體工程師]]和毛髮模擬專家凱莉·華德（{{lang|en|Kelly Ward}}）<ref name="clustrward">{{cite web|title=‘Tangled’ Hair Demo with Kelly Ward|url=http://clustr.com/news/detail/tangled_hair_demo_with_kelly_ward|work=Clustr|publisher=Clustr|accessdate=2013-06-22|date=2011-07-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141103224552/http://clustr.com/news/detail/tangled_hair_demo_with_kelly_ward|archivedate=2014-11-03}}</ref>負責製作特殊軟體，來協助動畫師們創造樂佩的長髮<ref name="mooreteenhollywood">{{cite web|last=Barker|first=Lynn|title=EXCLUSIVE INTERVIEW: We're "Tangled" with Mandy Moore!|url=http://www.teenhollywood.com/2010/09/17/we-re-tangled-with-mandy-moore|work=TeenHollywood.com|publisher=TeenHollywood.com II Inc|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2010-09-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141103230943/http://www.teenhollywood.com/2010/09/17/we-re-tangled-with-mandy-moore|archivedate=2014-11-03}}</ref>。華德表示在真實世界中，70英呎的長髮將會重達60[[磅|磅]]（27[[公斤|公斤]]），「重到無法使一個真人能像我們讓樂佩在電影中那樣地擺動自如」<ref name="kellywardncfilm">{{cite web|title=UNC Grad Student Untangles CGI Hair|url=http://www.ncfilm.com/news/498/109/UNC-Grad-Student-Untangles-CGI-Hair.html|work=North Carolina Film Office|publisher=North Carolina Film Office|accessdate=2013-06-22|date=2010-11-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104054943/http://www.ncfilm.com/news/498/109/UNC-Grad-Student-Untangles-CGI-Hair.html|archivedate=2013-11-04}}</ref>。為了簡單起見，動畫師保留了頭髮在外觀上的擬真程度，但減少了表面內部包含的髮絲數量以便於控制<ref name="nprrapunzelhair">{{cite web|last=Flatow|first=Ira|title=Untangling The Hairy Physics Of Rapunzel|url=http://www.npr.org/2012/04/20/151047258/untangling-the-hairy-physics-of-rapunzel|work=National Public Radio|publisher=NPR|accessdate=2013-06-22|date=2012-04-20|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104053518/http://www.npr.org/2012/04/20/151047258/untangling-the-hairy-physics-of-rapunzel|archivedate=2013-11-04}}</ref>。而為了要替長髮調出顯得獨特、同時卻又不失真實的金黃色澤，動畫師也在這方面遇到了一番挑戰<ref name="tangledhairvariety">{{cite web|last=Idelson|first=Karen|title=Rapunzel's do took years of software development|url=http://variety.com/2011/digital/news/tangled-tresses-tough-task-1118029497/|work=Variety|publisher=Variety Media, LLC|accessdate=2013-06-22|date=2011-01-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110140924/http://variety.com/2011/digital/news/tangled-tresses-tough-task-1118029497/|archivedate=2013-11-10}}</ref>。

