樂佩公主一角在大部分的評論裡都很受到歡迎。《{{Link-en|票房雜誌|Boxoffice (magazine)}}》的莎拉·維茲卡隆多（{{lang|en|Sara Vizcarrondo}}）喜歡這個角色，形容她「是位活力十足的女主角，以活水浸潤了嚴謹的公主角色典型」<ref name="boxofficerapunzel">{{cite web|last=Vizcarrondo|first=Sara|title=Tangled|url=http://www.boxoffice.com/reviews/2010-11-tangled?q=Tangled|work=Boxoffice|publisher=BOXOFFICE Media, LLC|accessdate=2013-03-13|date=2010-11-09}}</ref>。紐澤西《{{lang|en|明星紀事報|The Star-Ledger}}》的史蒂芬·惠迪（{{lang|en|Stephen Whitty}}）形容該角色是「一位才華洋溢的年輕女子」<ref name="whittytangled">{{cite web|last=Whitty|first=Stephen|title='Tangled' review: Disney returns to its magical roots with this golden girl|url=http://www.nj.com/entertainment/movies/index.ssf/2010/11/tangled_review_disney_returns_to_its_magical_roots_with_this_golden_girl.html|work=The Star-Ledger|publisher=New Jersey On-Line LLC|accessdate=2013-06-15|date=2010-11-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105200738/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/movies/index.ssf/2010/11/tangled_review_disney_returns_to_its_magical_roots_with_this_golden_girl.html|archivedate=2013-11-05}}</ref>。《洛杉磯時報》的{{Link-en|肯尼斯·杜蘭|Kenneth Turan}}也在文中表示樂佩「是位具有現代感的年輕女子」<ref name="tangledlatimes">{{cite web|last=Turan|first=Kenneth|title=Movie review: 'Tangled'|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2010/nov/24/entertainment/la-et-et-tangled-20101124|work=Los Angeles Times|publisher=Los Angeles Times|accessdate=2013-03-12|date=2010-11-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121224001131/http://articles.latimes.com/2010/nov/24/entertainment/la-et-et-tangled-20101124|archivedate=2012-12-24}}</ref>。《[[紐約客|紐約客]]》的布魯斯·迪奥内斯（{{lang|en|Bruce Diones}}）形容樂佩「有與生俱來的慧黠和靈敏的關懷力，而又不會顯得像個聒噪的青少女」<ref name="rapunzelnewyorker">{{cite web|last=Diones|first=Bruce|title=Tangled|url=http://www.newyorker.com/arts/reviews/film/tangled_howard|work=The New Yorker|publisher=Condé Nast|accessdate=2013-03-13|year=2010|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121111022924/http://www.newyorker.com/arts/reviews/film/tangled_howard|archivedate=2012-11-11}}</ref>。《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》的克勞蒂亞·普伊格（{{lang|en|Claudia Puig}}）則在文中指出，與之前數位年齡相仿的迪士尼公主相比，「樂佩扮演的青少年角色顯得較為可信」<ref name="usatodayrapunzel">{{cite web|last=Puig|first=Claudia|title='Tangled' gently teases Disney and its animated films|url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2010-11-24-tangled24_ST_N.htm|work=USA Today|publisher=Gannett Co. Inc|accessdate=2013-03-13|date=2010-11-26|archive-date=2017-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171208215045/https://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2010-11-24-tangled24_ST_N.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在其他將樂佩與先前諸位迪士尼公主相比的評論中。《[[紐約每日新聞|紐約每日新聞]]》的喬·紐瑪爾（{{lang|en|Joe Neumaier}}）將樂佩的獨立自主與[[美女與野獸|美女與野獸]]中的貝兒相作比較<ref name="dailynewsrapunzel">{{cite web|last=Neumaier|first=Joe|title='Tangled' review: Mandy Moore's Rapunzel is chill Disney retelling of classic hair-raising tale|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/tangled-review-mandy-moore-rapunzel-chill-disney-retelling-classic-hair-raising-tale-article-1.455647|work=Daily News|publisher=NYDailyNews.com|accessdate=2013-03-13|date=2010-11-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130817072203/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/tangled-review-mandy-moore-rapunzel-chill-disney-retelling-classic-hair-raising-tale-article-1.455647|archivedate=2013-08-17}}</ref>。英國《{{Link-en|完全電影|Total Film}}》雜誌的強納森·克羅克（{{lang|en|Jonathan Crocker}}）指出了樂佩與愛麗兒的相似性，形容前者是「一位意志堅強的女主角，渴望能一睹外頭的世界」<ref name="rapunzeltotalfilm">{{cite web|last=Crocker|first=Jonathan|title=Tangled Disney has a good hair day…|url=http://www.totalfilm.com/reviews/cinema/tangled|work=Total Film|publisher=Future Publishing Limited|accessdate=2013-03-12|date=2011-01-14|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130308013344/http://www.totalfilm.com/reviews/cinema/tangled|archivedate=2013-03-08}}</ref>。紐澳良《{{Link-en|時代瑣聞報|The Times-Picayune}}》的麥可·史考特（{{lang|en|Mike Scott}}） 在文中表示樂佩的無邪「讓人想起[[艾美·亞當斯|艾美·亞當斯]]在[[曼哈頓奇緣|曼哈頓奇緣]]中，飾演的那位天真爛漫的公主吉賽兒」<ref name="nolarapunzel">{{cite web|last=Scott|first=Mike|title='Tangled' is a return to princess-ly roots for Disney Animation|url=http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2010/11/tangled_is_a_return_to_princes.html|work=The Times-Picayune|publisher=New Orleans Net LLC|accessdate=2013-03-13|date=2010-11-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511220301/http://www.nola.com/movies/index.ssf/2010/11/tangled_is_a_return_to_princes.html|archivedate=2013-05-11}}</ref>。影評人湯姆·查瑞帝（{{lang|en|Tom Charity}}） 則將樂佩的獨立自主同時與愛麗兒和[[花木蘭_(1998年電影)|花木蘭]]相比，並提到樂佩「替迪士尼近年慣例下的豪放不拘型女主角中，再添一例」<ref name="rapunzellovefilm">{{cite web|last=Charity|first=Tom|title=Tangled Review|url=http://www.lovefilm.com/reviews/Tangled|work=LoveFilm|publisher=Amazon.com, Inc|accessdate=2013-03-13|date=2011-01-24|quote=|archive-date=2018-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180321124329/https://www.amazon.co.uk/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=202167400|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

也有部分影評對樂佩顯示出的好感較少。《[[時代週刊|時代週刊]]》的{{Link-en|理查·柯里斯|Richard Corliss}}儘管很喜歡魔髮奇緣這部電影，卻覺得聚焦於費林·雷德的部分太多，而對樂佩的著墨不足。他寫道：「60年來...女孩子是被期待能長大、克服困境、變得更有擔當的角心人物」，但「[[皮克斯|皮克斯]]、[[夢工廠|夢工廠]]等工作室卻破壞了這些以女性為核心的電影」<ref name="rapunzeltime">{{cite news|last=Corliss|first=Richard|title=Tangled: Disney's Ripping Rapunzel|url=http://www.time.com/time/arts/article/0,8599,2033166,00.html|work=Time|publisher=Time Inc|accessdate=2013-03-12|date=2010-11-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130225082105/http://www.time.com/time/arts/article/0,8599,2033166,00.html|archivedate=2013-02-25}}</ref>。{{lang|en|Reelviews.net}}網的線上影評人{{Link-en|詹姆斯·伯納汀内里|James Berardinelli}}表示樂佩「雖然很可愛又活潑，但仍不如[[白雪公主|白雪公主]]、愛麗兒或貝兒來得令人印象深刻」<ref name="rapunzelberardinelli">{{cite web|last=Berardinelli|first=James|title=Tangled|url=http://www.reelviews.net/php_review_template.php?identifier=2215|work=ReelViews|publisher=James Berardinelli|accessdate=2013-03-13|date=2010-11-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023143351/http://www.reelviews.net/php_review_template.php?identifier=2215|archivedate=2012-10-23}}</ref>。

===褒揚與獲獎===
[[CNN|CNN]]的史蒂芬妮·郭德堡（{{lang|en|Stephanie Goldberg}}）在文章《[[勇敢傳說|勇敢傳說]]的[[梅莉達公主|梅莉達]]與其他動畫女角》裡，將樂佩列在迪士尼幾位最英勇而獨立的女主角中<ref name="cnnheroines">{{cite news|last=Goldberg|first=Stephanie|title='Brave's' Merida and other animated heroines|url=http://www.cnn.com/2012/06/22/showbiz/movies/brave-merida-animated-heroines|work=CNN|publisher=Cable News Network|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2012-06-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921055940/http://www.cnn.com/2012/06/22/showbiz/movies/brave-merida-animated-heroines|archivedate=2013-09-21}}</ref>。線上雜誌{{lang|en|{{Link-en|Nerve.com|Nerve.com}}}}的莎萊雅（{{lang|en|Sonia Saraiya}}） 在文章《排行榜：最柔弱到最自主的迪士尼公主們》中把樂佩排到第四名，將她活潑的性格與上一代迪士尼公主中的愛麗兒和《[[阿拉丁_(電影)|阿拉丁]]》裡的茉莉公主（{{lang|en|Jasmine}}）比較。莎萊雅形容樂佩是個「悍女子」，儘管「她的天真有時牴觸了她先進的性格」。又說「她也察覺了所處的困境裡有所不公，並且找到了突破的方法，以智謀擺脫了她的『媽媽』——實為綁架她的人——，而到外面的世界探險」<ref name="rapunzelnerverank">{{cite web|last=Saraiya|first=Sonia|title=Ranked: Disney Princesses From Least To Most Feminist|url=http://www.nerve.com/entertainment/ranked/ranked-disney-princesses-from-least-to-most-feminist?page=2|work=Nerve|publisher=Nerve.com Inc|accessdate=2013-03-13|date=2012-07-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151231022021/http://www.nerve.com/entertainment/ranked/ranked-disney-princesses-from-least-to-most-feminist|archivedate=2015-12-31}}</ref>。[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]女性網站「{{lang|en|Female Network}}」的戴里特（{{lang|en|Tala Dayrit}}）在文章《30位威猛和有趣的卡通女角》中，提到樂佩與原典中的「長髮姑娘」相去甚遠，「她並非無助、鎖在塔裡枯等未知命運的嬌弱閨女，而是位可以在打鬥中捍衛自己的堅強女子」<ref name="femalenetwork">{{cite web|last=Dayrit|first=Tala|title=30 Fierce and Fun Female Cartoon Characters|url=http://www.femalenetwork.com/travel-leisure/30-fierce-and-fun-female-cartoon-characters|work=Female Network|publisher=Summit Digital|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2011-03-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130702051842/http://www.femalenetwork.com/travel-leisure/30-fierce-and-fun-female-cartoon-characters|archivedate=2013-07-02}}</ref>。

樂佩在片中與尤金的愛情對唱曲《{{lang|en|[[I_See_the_Light|I See the Light]]}}》也得到許多好評，獲得[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]的{{Link-en|葛萊美最佳影視媒體作品歌曲獎|Grammy Award for Best Song Written for Visual Media|最佳影視媒體作品歌曲獎}}及[[拉斯维加斯影评人协会|拉斯維加斯影評人協會獎]]的最佳歌曲獎<ref name="grammyplaybill">{{cite web|last=Gans|first=Andrew|title=Alan Menken and Glenn Slater Win Grammy Award|url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/159598-Alan-Menken-and-Glenn-Slater-Win-Grammy-Award|work=Playbill|publisher=Playbill, Inc|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2012-02-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810184145/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/159598-Alan-Menken-and-Glenn-Slater-Win-Grammy-Award|archivedate=2014-08-10}}</ref><ref name="grammybroadwayworld">{{cite web|title=Alan Menken and Glenn Slater Receive Grammy Award for TANGLED's 'I See the Light'|url=http://broadwayworld.com/article/Alan-Menken-and-Glenn-Slater-Receive-Grammy-Award-for-TANGLEDs-I-See-the-Light-20120212|work=Broadway World.com|publisher=Wisdom Digital Media|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2012-02-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053652/http://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Alan-Menken-and-Glenn-Slater-Receive-Grammy-Award-for-TANGLEDs-I-See-the-Light-20120212|archivedate=2013-09-21}}</ref>、亦曾被[[奧斯卡最佳原創歌曲獎|奧斯卡最佳原創歌曲獎]]及[[第83屆奧斯卡金像獎|第83屆奧斯卡金像獎]]提名<ref name="tangledoscars">{{cite web|title=83rd Academy Award Nominations|url=http://variety.com/2011/scene/news/83rd-academy-award-nominations-1118030824/|work=Variety|publisher=Variety Media, LLC|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=January 25, 201|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053629/http://variety.com/2011/scene/news/83rd-academy-award-nominations-1118030824/|archivedate=2013-09-21}}</ref><ref name="mtvoscars">{{cite web|last=Anderson|first=Kyle|title=The Oscar Nominations: Handicapping The Best Original Song Category|url=http://newsroom.mtv.com/2011/01/25/oscar-nominations-best-original-song/|work=MTV|publisher=Viacom International Inc|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2011-01-25|archive-date=2013-06-28|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130628042212/http://newsroom.mtv.com/2011/01/25/oscar-nominations-best-original-song/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="menkenbroadway">{{cite web|last=Henderson|first=Kathy|title=Alan Menken on His 19th Oscar Nomination: 'I Never Take It for Granted'|url=http://www.broadway.com/buzz/155017/alan-menken-on-his-19th-oscar-nomination-i-never-take-it-for-granted/|work=Broadway.com|publisher=BROADWAY.COM|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2011-01-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053416/http://www.broadway.com/buzz/155017/alan-menken-on-his-19th-oscar-nomination-i-never-take-it-for-granted/|archivedate=2013-09-21}}</ref>。

