===迪士尼公主與相關商品===
樂佩成為第10位[[迪士尼公主|迪士尼公主]]後<ref name="princess rapunzel">{{cite web|url=http://www.stitchkingdom.com/disney-rapunzel-kensington-palace-16502/|title=Rapunzel to Receive Coronation Ceremony October 2 at Kensington Palace|date=2011-06-14|work=Stitch Kingdom|accessdate=2011-06-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/664sj4e3N?url=http://www.stitchkingdom.com/disney-rapunzel-kensington-palace-16502/|archivedate=2012年3月11日|df=}}</ref>，針對以少女為主的消費族群推出了玩具、影音錄製品、服裝和[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]等週邊系列產品<ref name="whatswrongwithcinderella">{{cite news|last=Orenstein|first=Peggy|title=What’s Wrong With Cinderella?|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/12/24/magazine/24princess.t.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0|work=The New York Times|publisher=The New York Times Company|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2006-12-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130627135034/http://www.nytimes.com/2006/12/24/magazine/24princess.t.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0|archivedate=2013-06-27}}</ref>。[[華特迪士尼公司|華特迪士尼公司]]透過[[加冕|加冕]]將角色排入迪士尼公主行列，而樂佩的加冕典禮於2011年10月2日在[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]的[[肯辛頓宮|肯辛頓宮]]舉辦<ref name="rapunzelprincessattractions">{{cite web|last=Roseboom|first=Matt|title=Rapunzel named 10th Disney Princess in ceremony at Kensington Palace in London|url=http://attractionsmagazine.com/blog/2011/10/05/rapunzel-named-10th-disney-princess-in-ceremony-at-kensington-palace-in-london/|work=Orlando Attractions Magazine|publisher=Orlando Attractions Magazine|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2011-10-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130529131319/http://attractionsmagazine.com/blog/2011/10/05/rapunzel-named-10th-disney-princess-in-ceremony-at-kensington-palace-in-london/|archivedate=2013-05-29}}</ref><ref name="princessrapunzelabout">{{cite web|last=Bryson|first=Carey|title=Rapunzel Induction Ceremony This Weekend|url=http://kidstvmovies.about.com/b/2011/09/30/rapunzel-induction-ceremony-this-weekend.htm|work=About.com|publisher=About.com|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2011-09-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513224956/http://kidstvmovies.about.com/b/2011/09/30/rapunzel-induction-ceremony-this-weekend.htm|archivedate=2013-05-13}}</ref><ref name="grenohowardabout">{{cite web|last=Molina|first=Melissa|title=Exclusive Interview with 'Tangled' Directors Byron Howard and Nathan Greno|url=http://movies.about.com/od/rapunzel/a/Tangled-Directors-Byron-Howard-Nathan-Greno.htm|work=About.com|publisher=About.com|accessdate=2013-06-25|year=2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130803083407/http://movies.about.com/od/rapunzel/a/Tangled-Directors-Byron-Howard-Nathan-Greno.htm|archivedate=2013-08-03}}</ref>，這也是肯辛頓宮首次舉行「虛擬」公主的加冕儀式<ref>[http://xmwb.xinmin.cn/xmwb/html/2011-10/28/content_70_1.htm 女英雄“長髮公主”樂佩] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130925183620/http://xmwb.xinmin.cn/xmwb/html/2011-10/28/content_70_1.htm |date=2013-09-25 }}－《[[新民晚報|新民晚報]]》數字報</ref>。然而在許多相關產品中，樂佩是使用傳統動畫繪製的版本呈現<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.therotoscopers.com/2013/04/29/merida-to-officially-be-coronated-as-disney-princess-gets-new-look/|title = Merida To Officially Be Coronated As Disney Princess, Gets New Look|first = Gay|last = Wright|accessdate = 2013-07-09|date = 2013-04-29|publisher = The Rotoscopers|website = The Rotoscopers|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130507095646/http://www.therotoscopers.com/2013/04/29/merida-to-officially-be-coronated-as-disney-princess-gets-new-look/|archivedate = 2013-05-07}}</ref>。隨著加冕典禮舉辦之後，迪士尼公主英文版官網上也增設了她的頁面<ref name="rapunzeldisneyprincesswebsite">{{cite web|title=Rapunzel|url=http://princess.disney.com/rapunzel|work=Disney Princess|publisher=Disney|accessdate=2013-06-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130730171353/http://princess.disney.com/rapunzel|archivedate=2013-07-30}}</ref>。

{{Link-en|迪士尼消費品部|Disney Consumer Products}}<ref>{{cite web|title = Head of Disney Consumer Products group steps down|date = 2011-09-06|first = Dawn C.|last = Chmielewski|work = Los Angeles Times|publisher = Los Angeles Times|accessdate = 2013-07-02|url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/entertainmentnewsbuzz/2011/09/head-of-disney-consumer-products-group-steps-down.html|deadurl = no|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131001220037/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/entertainmentnewsbuzz/2011/09/head-of-disney-consumer-products-group-steps-down.html|archivedate = 2013-10-01}}</ref>迄今發行的許多產品中都有樂佩的登場<ref name="disney store">{{cite web|work=Disney Store|title=Tangled|url=http://www.disneystore.com/tangled/mn/1000052/|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101203010002/http://www.disneystore.com/tangled/mn/1000052/|archivedate=2010-12-03}}</ref>，例如在一套名為「{{Link-en|迪士尼魔髮奇緣 (電子遊戲)|Tangled: The Video Game|迪士尼魔髮奇緣}}」的[[冒險遊戲|冒險遊戲]]中<ref name="platformnationtangled">{{cite web|last=Forbis|first=Chris|title=Disney’s Tangled: The Video Game Review (DS)|url=http://www.platformnation.com/2010/12/12/disneys-tangled-the-video-game-review-ds/|work=Platform Nation|publisher=Platform Nation|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2010-12-12|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923041718/http://www.platformnation.com/2010/12/12/disneys-tangled-the-video-game-review-ds/|archivedate=2013-09-23}}</ref>，樂佩被設定為玩家可操控角色<ref name="gamershelltangled">{{cite web|title=Disney Tangled: The Video Game Released and Screens #2|url=http://www.gamershell.com/news_106932.html|work=GamersHell.com|publisher=GamersHell.com|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2010-11-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130925114435/http://www.gamershell.com/news_106932.html|archivedate=2013-09-25}}</ref><ref name="tanglednintendo">{{cite web|title=Disney Tangled: The Video Game|url=http://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/1iFvsK4hQb006GMh6uVgQGEAEleEmoSE|work=Nintendo|publisher=Nintendo|accessdate=2013-06-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130706235749/http://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/1iFvsK4hQb006GMh6uVgQGEAEleEmoSE|archivedate=2013-07-06}}</ref>。該電玩由{{Link-en|迪士尼互動工作室|Disney Interactive Studios}}發行於2010年11月23日，比電影的上映日還早一天，遊戲內容則依據電影情節設計，適用於[[Nintendo_Wii|Wii]]和[[Nintendo_DS|DS]]等[[任天堂|任天堂]][[電子遊戲|電子遊戲平台]]<ref name=platformnationtangled/><ref name="video game">{{cite web|work=Disney Dreaming|title=Disney Interactive Studios "Tangled" Video Game|url=http://www.disneydreaming.com/2010/08/07/disney-interactive-studios-tangled-video-game/|date=2010-08-07|accessdate=2013-04-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923013328/http://www.disneydreaming.com/2010/08/07/disney-interactive-studios-tangled-video-game/|archivedate=2013-09-23}} Tangled Video Game.</ref>。電玩中的樂佩依然錄用了曼蒂·摩爾的配音<ref name="gamershellpressrelease">{{cite web|title=Disney Interactive Studios Invites Players to Swing into an Exciting, Hair-Raising Adventure with Disney Tangled: The Video Game|url=http://www.gamershell.com/companies/disney_interactive/797258.html|work=GamersHell.com|publisher=GamersHell.com|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2010-11-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130626064559/http://www.gamershell.com/companies/disney_interactive/797258.html|archivedate=2013-06-26}}</ref>，而她本人也對此感到很自豪<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.worldjournal.com/view/full_entertainment/10059504/article-%E8%90%8A%E5%A8%81%EF%BC%9A%E9%95%B7%E9%AB%AE%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E6%AF%94%E6%91%A9%E7%88%BE%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E4%BA%BA?instance=en_bull_us |title=世界新聞網-北美華文新聞、華商資訊 - 萊威：長髮公主比摩爾吸引人 |accessdate=2013-09-22 |archive-date=2013-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130926045909/http://www.worldjournal.com/view/full_entertainment/10059504/article-%E8%90%8A%E5%A8%81%EF%BC%9A%E9%95%B7%E9%AB%AE%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E6%AF%94%E6%91%A9%E7%88%BE%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E4%BA%BA?instance=en_bull_us |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

此外，樂佩也被製成多個[[洋娃娃|洋娃娃]]產品，在「迪士尼動畫師收藏系列」（{{lang|en|Disney Animator's Collection}}）中11位幼兒時期版的迪士尼公主娃娃裡面，也是第一位推出的角色。該系列的洋娃娃均由葛連·基恩和馬克·韓恩（{{lang|en|Mark Henn}}）兩位迪士尼動畫師參與設計<ref>{{cite web|url = http://blog.disneystore.com/blog/princess/page/2/|date = 2011-12-19|work = Disney Store|publisher = Disney|accessdate = 2013-07-02|title = Enter to win the Top Toy of the Holiday Season: Disney Animators’ Collection Toddler Doll!|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130510022351/http://blog.disneystore.com/blog/princess/page/2/|archivedate = 2013-05-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title = Creating a princess|work = ToyNews|first = Lewis|accessdate = 2013-07-02|date = 2012-04-16|publisher = Intent Media|last = Tyler|url = http://www.toynews-online.biz/business-analysis/read/creating-a-princess/030560|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130926051006/http://www.toynews-online.biz/business-analysis/read/creating-a-princess/030560|archivedate = 2013-09-26}} Retrieved 2 July 30.</ref>。

===迪士尼主題樂園及宣傳作品===
樂佩在全球數個[[華特迪士尼樂園及度假區|華特迪士尼樂園及度假區]]裡都有出現過<ref name="rapunzeldisneyparks">{{cite web|title=Rapunzel and Flynn Rider|url=http://disneyland.disney.go.com/disneyland/tangled/|work=Disney Park|publisher=Disney|accessdate=2013-06-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130527023557/http://disneyland.disney.go.com/disneyland/tangled/|archivedate=2013-05-27}}</ref>。而[[佛羅里達|佛羅里達]][[華特迪士尼世界度假區|華特迪士尼世界度假區]]及[[迪士尼樂園|加州迪士尼樂園]]裡更設立了數座遊樂設施，仿造電影中樂佩活動過的場景<ref name="rapunzelparks">{{cite web|last=Charles|first=Ayesha|title=Tangled Inspirations at the Disney Parks!|url=http://www.attraction-tickets-direct.co.uk/california/latest-news/tangled-inspirations-disney-parks|work=Attraction Tickets Direct|publisher=Attraction Tickets Direct|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2013-02-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928061027/http://www.attraction-tickets-direct.co.uk/california/latest-news/tangled-inspirations-disney-parks|archivedate=2013-09-28}}</ref>，當中還包括了位於佛羅里達的迪士尼[[幻想世界|神奇王國]]、以真實比例建成了樂佩居住的高塔<ref name="rapunzeltower">{{cite web|title=Fantasyland Update: Rapunzel's Tall Tower (PART 1)|url=http://www.orlandoparksnews.com/2012/12/fantasyland-update-rapunzels-tall-tower.html|work=Orlando Theme Park News|publisher=Orlando Theme Park News|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2012-12-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130726022008/http://www.orlandoparksnews.com/2012/12/fantasyland-update-rapunzels-tall-tower.html|archivedate=2013-07-26}}</ref>。

在[[安妮·萊柏維茲|安妮·萊柏維茲]]為宣傳迪士尼樂園及度假區的活動「百萬夢想年」（{{lang|en|Year of a Million Dreams}}），而於2007年起<ref name="disneydreamportrait">{{cite web|title=Taylor Swift doubles as Rapunzel: Annie Leibovitz's Disney Dream Portraits|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/annie-leibovitz-disney-dream-portraits-gallery-1.7401|work=Daily News|publisher=NYDailyNews.com|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2013-01-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130520125714/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/annie-leibovitz-disney-dream-portraits-gallery-1.7401|archivedate=2013-05-20}}</ref>拍攝的「{{Link-en|迪士尼夢想肖像系列|Disney Dream Portrait Series}}」寫真作品中，由美國鄉村音樂女歌手[[泰勒絲|泰勒絲]]在2013年宣傳照「冒險之旅將起於此」（{{lang|en|Where a world of adventure awaits}}）裡化身為真人版的樂佩<ref name="自由時報">[http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/jan/25/today-show24.htm 自由電子報 - 泰勒絲變魔髮 釣哈利回頭] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130302190102/http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2013/new/jan/25/today-show24.htm |date=2013-03-02 }}</ref><ref name="swiftrapunzelotrc">{{cite web|last=Heller|first=Corinne|title=Taylor Swift is Rapunzel in Annie Leibovitz's new Disney Dream Portrait (Photo)|url=http://www.ontheredcarpet.com/Taylor-Swift-is-Rapunzel-in-Annie-Leibovitzs-new-Disney-Dream-Portrait-Photo/8965382|work=On The Red Carpet|publisher=OnTheRedCarpet.com|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2013-01-23|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528141806/http://www.ontheredcarpet.com/Taylor-Swift-is-Rapunzel-in-Annie-Leibovitzs-new-Disney-Dream-Portrait-Photo/8965382|archivedate=2013-05-28}}</ref>。《{{Link-en|Us週刊|Us Weekly}}》對該攝影作品的圖片說明寫道：「在這張標題為『冒險之旅將起於此』、且令人摒息的寫真裡，這位23歲的葛萊美獎得主倚靠在一座滿佈蘚苔的塔窗邊。當她若有所思地望向遠方時，粉色的襯裙從紫色長裙下探出，金色長髮華麗地流洩在空中。」<ref name="swiftrapunzelusweekly">{{cite web|last=Takeda|first=Allison|title=Taylor Swift Poses as Rapunzel in New Disney Ad by Annie Leibovitz: Picture|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/taylor-swift-poses-as-rapunzel-in-new-disney-ad-by-annie-leibovitz-picture-2013231|work=Us Weekly|publisher=Us Weekly|accessdate=2013-06-25|date=2013-01-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130616033735/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/taylor-swift-poses-as-rapunzel-in-new-disney-ad-by-annie-leibovitz-picture-2013231|archivedate=2013-06-16}}</ref>泰勒絲之後向娛樂新聞「{{Link-en|紅毯秀|On The Red Carpet}}」（{{lang|en|OTRC}}）表示自己很榮幸能被選為宣傳照的女主角<ref name=swiftrapunzelotrc/>。

